				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Twisting Songs<a name="74563"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 17 05 3:29 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>To twist songs I set my keyboard as follows:
<br />
I set the W to Forward, S to Backup, D to turn right, A to turn left. I found it easy to twist songs by using the Q &amp; E keys along with the 2 &amp; 3 keys. With this setup I am able to keep 3 songs going and even throw in a 4th as the keys are all close together. When traveling it is simple to set the Q &amp; E keys to SOW &amp; Health for example and control my movement with one hand. Other hand is free for mouse or other keys.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"></span></td>
